Mercator Poslovni Sistem (MELR)  d.d. of
Slovenia is in talks to acquire Serbian retailers Familija
Market d.o.o. and Jabuka a.d., Finance newspaper  reported 
without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
